flowchart TB
    X[clean image x] --> G[Generator G_phi<br/>~5.35M params, U-Net]
    G --> DELTA[tanh-projected delta<br/>bounded by eps]
    X --> ADD((+))
    DELTA --> ADD
    ADD --> XP[perturbed x + delta]
    XP --> EOT[EOT wrapper T<br/>resize / blur / diff-JPEG]
    EOT --> TARGETS{Ensemble surrogates}
    TARGETS --> RET[RetinaFace R50<br/>detection loss]
    TARGETS --> ARC[ArcFace IR-100<br/>ID cosine loss]
    TARGETS --> SD15[SD 1.5 VAE<br/>gray-latent loss]
    TARGETS --> SDXL[SDXL VAE<br/>gray-latent loss]
    TARGETS --> CLIP[CLIP ViT-B/32<br/>cosine loss]
    XP --> RSAMP[RestorerSampler<br/>identity / SD1.5-VAE / GFPGAN 1.4]
    RSAMP --> RXP[R x + delta]
    X --> RSAMP2[same R]
    RSAMP2 --> RX[R x]
    RXP --> LPIPS[LPIPS distance]
    RX --> LPIPS
    LPIPS -->|negative weight| LOSS
    RET --> LOSS[CompositeLoss L]
    ARC --> LOSS
    SD15 --> LOSS
    SDXL --> LOSS
    CLIP --> LOSS
    LOSS -->|backprop| G
